import React from 'react'; import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next'; import { useQuery } from 'react-query'; import apiService from '../services/apiService'; import LoadingSpinner from '../components/LoadingSpinner'; const AdminDashboard = () => { const { t } = useTranslation(); const { data: stats, isLoading: statsLoading } = useQuery( 'adminStats', apiService.getDashboardStats ); if (statsLoading) return ; return (

{t('adminDashboard')}

{/* Stats Grid */}
{t('totalProjects')}
{stats?.total_projects || 0}
{t('pendingApprovals')}
{stats?.pending_approvals || 0}
{t('totalFunding')}
${stats?.total_funding?.toLocaleString() || 0}
{t('totalUsers')}
{stats?.total_users || 0}
{/* Quick Actions */}

{t('userManagement')}

{t('manageUsers')}

{t('projectApproval')}

{t('approveProjects')}

{t('verificationMonitoring')}

{t('monitorVerifications')}

{t('auditLogs')}

{t('viewAuditLogs')}

{/* Recent Activity */}

{t('recentActivity')}

{t('noRecentActivity')}

{t('activityWillAppearHere')}

); }; export default AdminDashboard;
